successes.title: New Five Iron Frenzy Album!!!!
successes.description:
Hey,
Some might call it beating a dead horse. We call it recording an album. Help us!

Pledges.description: Our thanks and a virtual high five. Much like an imaginary high five!
A new limited edition sticker. How fun is that? You can stick it on yer face!
Advance download of album (2 weeks before street date) Street date = release date. A date is a fruit.
A physical copy of the CD that can be used as a drink coaster + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date
Single drum stick autographed by Andy Verdecchio. You may have seen him on stage during a Five Iron concert behind the drums. + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date
Very limited vintage 8x10 photograph of Five Iron pic. Autographed. You might get the one of Andy as a ghost! It's creepy
+ advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date
A CD!!! Signed by all band members who are willing to sign. Were talkin' like at least 7 of the members! + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date
Limited edition t-shirt + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date
Limited edition onesies to 5T (for those of you without kids this means kids clothes. These are sizes) + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date
Post cards from each member of the band with a personal message. You get 8 post cards! + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date.
New record on record (vinyl) + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date.

Give Reese a wedgie

Five Iron Care Package to include an assortment of goodies. Includes an EP of new silly songs, some of our favorite snacks, a limited edition t-shirt, a couple of stickers. + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date

Kickstarter exclusive show!!! 
Come see us at our first concert in 8 years.
It will be in Denver - Date and Venue TBD. We will give you at least 2 months notice. + advanced digital download of album 2 weeks before street date.
VIP package for TWO to Joshua Fest (Plymouth, CA, you get there on your own)

This pass includes full weekend passes, full weekend catering (breakfast, lunch and dinner) with the artists, full backstage access for the the day that FIF plays, and full access to the artist lounge. Also includes Free Festival T-Shirts, and other JFest merch.
Valued at $300
Aug. 31 - Sept. 2 -- http://www.joshuafest.com/2012
